description: If you have a difficult decision to make then let Alexa decide for you.  Especially those tough question that your friends are too shy to answer for you.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask Choice Master if I should call my ex.
Alexa, ask Choice Master if I should put on pants today.
Alexa, ask Choice Master if I should call in sick.
name: Choice Master
shortDescription: Ask Alexa if you should do something or you shouldn't
